title: Great location! Bright 3BR 2BA apt, Stainless kitchen, Large window
posting_body: ['Our spacious studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments are noticeably larger than neighboring apartment communities.', 'With a large air conditioned living room, private deck and ceiling fans, mirrored closet doors and built-in closet organizers in every bedroom, you’ll be living in comfort.', 'This apartment features:', 'Bright, large window in living room', 'Lots of natural afternoon sunlight', 'Air-conditioned comfort', 'Fully-equipped kitchen with stove, refrigerator, dishwasher & disposal', 'Quartz countertops', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Wood-style flooring throughout', '12 month lease available', 'Come Visit us!', 'Park Terrace', '860 Quince Ave', 'Santa Clara, CA 95051', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday - Friday 9:00AM to 6:00PM', 'Saturday 9:00AM – 2:00PM', 'Closed Sunday & Monday', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: santa clara, hwy 280, lawrence expy, san tomas expy, kaiser, pets, santa clara unified school district, pomeroy elementary, cabrillo middle school, santa clara high school']
